# Carrick ‚Äî Webflow + Commerce7 (C7)

Webflow site with Commerce7 integration. **Not Next.js.** There is no app build step ‚Äî only CSS and JS assets.

## Constraints

- No access to the C7 backend or admin. All UI changes are done with CSS/JS against C7-rendered DOM.
- C7 owns all routes under `/profile` (e.g. `/profile`, `/profile/login`, `/profile/account`).
- Staging URL: https://carrick-6a9492.webflow.io/profile
- C7 loads via: `https://cdn.commerce7.com/beta/commerce7.js` (`data-tenant="carrick-winery"`).
- C7 swaps views client-side ‚Äî site-wide scripts must use `MutationObserver` and survive DOM re-renders.
- Scope styles with `body:has(.c7-‚Ä¶)` selectors so rules apply after C7 injects markup.
- Font `@import` for Albert Sans lives in the Webflow site head ‚Äî do not duplicate in CSS files.

## Hosting & deployment

Assets live in this repo and are served to Webflow via **jsDelivr** (GitHub CDN). The user pushes to GitHub; Webflow loads the files by URL. **Do not tell the user to copy-paste file contents into Webflow** ‚Äî only edit the source files here.

- **Repo:** https://github.com/cubdigital/carrick-c7.git
- **Branch:** `main`

### Webflow Site Settings ‚Üí Custom Code
**Head:**
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/sitewide.css">
```

**Footer:**
```html
<script defer type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.commerce7.com/beta/commerce7.js" id="c7-javascript" data-tenant="carrick-winery"></script>
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/sitewide.js"></script>
```

Profile-specific assets use the same CDN pattern when linked from the `/profile` page settings.

## Source files (edit these)

| File | Scope | Loaded from |
|------|-------|-------------|
| `sitewide.css` | Site-wide C7 overrides (login, profile, shared layout) | Site Settings ‚Üí Head |
| `sitewide.js` | Site-wide behaviour (age gate, profile/login DOM wrappers, observers) | Site Settings ‚Üí Footer |
| `profile-head.css` | `/profile` dashboard-only styles | `/profile` page ‚Üí Custom Code ‚Üí Head |
| `profile-before-body.html` | Legacy inline script ‚Äî prefer moving logic into `sitewide.js` or a `.js` file |

**Use `.css` and `.js` files only.** Do not create HTML wrapper files with `<script>` or `<style>` tags unless the user explicitly asks.

## Agent workflow

1. Edit the relevant `.css` or `.js` file directly.
2. Keep changes scoped and minimal ‚Äî match existing patterns in the file.
3. Remind the user to `git push` to `main` when done; Webflow picks up changes after jsDelivr cache refreshes (~minutes).
4. For an immediate CDN update, pin jsDelivr to a commit hash instead of `@main`.

## C7 DOM reference

Common selectors agents will target:

- Login: `.c7-account-login`
- Dashboard: `.c7-account__dashboard`, `.c7-account-tile__section`
- Custom wrappers added by our JS: `.carrick-dashboard-intro`, `.carrick-tile-row`, `.carrick-profile-layout`
